          <title>
            <string language="en">Naming of organic compounds</string>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Benennen der organischen Mittel</string>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">Nommer des composés organiques</string>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">Nomear de compostos orgânicos</string>

            <string language="x-mt-el">Ονομασία των οργανικών ενώσεων</string>

          </title>
          <description>
            <string language="en">This illustration shows the skeletal formula of 3-chloro-4,5-dimethylheptane, the structural formula of 1-methyl-3-nitrobenzene and the molecular formula of 2-bromoethanoic acid. This can be used for an exercise in naming organic compounds.</string>

          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Diese Abbildung zeigt die skelettartige Formel 
von 3-chloro-4,5-dimethylheptane, die strukturelle Formel von 
1-methyl-3-nitrobenzene und die molekulare Formel der Säure 
2-bromoethanoic. Dieses kann für eine Übung verwendet werden, 
wenn man organische Mittel benennt.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">Cette illustration montre la formule squelettique 
de 3-chloro-4,5-dimethylheptane, la formule structurale de 
1-methyl-3-nitrobenzene et la formule moléculaire de l'acide 
2-bromoethanoic. Ceci peut être utilisé pour un exercice en 
nommant les composés organiques.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">Esta ilustração mostra a fórmula esqueletal de
3-chloro-4,5-dimethylheptane, a fórmula estrutural de 
1-methyl-3-nitrobenzene e a fórmula molecular do ácido 
2-bromoethanoic. Isto pode ser usado para um exercício em 
nomear compostos orgânicos.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-it">Questa illustrazione mostra la formula 
scheletrica di 3-chloro-4,5-dimethylheptane, la formula strutturale di
1-methyl-3-nitrobenzene e la formula molecolare di acido 
2-bromoethanoic. Ciò può essere usata per un'esercitazione nel
chiamare i residui organici.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-el">Αυτή η απεικόνιση εμφανίζει το σκελετικό τύπο 
3-χλωρο, το δομικό τύπο του 1-μεθυλικός-3-νιτροβενζολίου και 
μοριακό τύπο του 2- bromoethanoic οξέος. Αυτό μπορεί να 
χρησιμοποιηθεί για μια άσκηση στην ονομασία των οργανικών 
ενώσεων.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-es">Esta ilustración muestra el fórmula esquelético
de 3-chloro-4,5-dimethylheptane, el fórmula estructural de 
1-methyl-3-nitrobenzene y el fórmula molecular del ácido 
2-bromoethanoic. Esto se puede utilizar para un ejercicio en el 
nombramiento de compuestos orgánicos.</string>
          </description>
